  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the time of the season, which was about six months during the year, the place grew to double the size because they came lot of people working in the thermal place, and they were not living in the-- in the holiday resort because it was small and very expensive.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were living in our village and went daily to their workplace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So maybe we had in this seasons sometimes 4,000, sometimes four and a half thousand people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what was the Jewish population-- the size of the Jewish population?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish population in my little [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Burs ?] town could have been-- I can only guess-- about 20, 25 families.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so the population was possibly 250 people-- souls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family-- then my father was a businessman, like, he was the owner of a country store, a general country store.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Samuel Hirschmann.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He established that shop of his, of his firm, before the first World War.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And must have been very diligent and able because he build it up to a very prosperous business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the place where-- where we had-- there we are living and we had the business was also important for the whole district because we had the sugar refinery there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole area, or the district of-- of Tepla or Teplice, was a sugar-growing district, and the-- the sugar refinery was established there by German Jewish people, which I found out later on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They must have been establishing this sugar refinery maybe about 30 to 40 years before the first World War.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was a well-established and well-known place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the reason why my father most probably decided to have a-- a, like, a general store, not a small grocery shop.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
